Download Geographic Data on Various Topics Provided and Managed by the Spatial Data Infrastructure of Peru

Introducction

This package provides R users with a new way to access Peruâ€™s official cartographic data on various topics that are managed by the Spatial Data Infrastructure of Peru.

Working with R

library(geoidep)
library(ggplot2)

Official Administrative Boundaries by INEI

departaments <- get_departaments(show_progress = FALSE)
